      <npc_text>You wait until dark and make your way to Lorenza’s villa. It’s a traditional building – single-storey for the most part, with a small tower in one corner, and an open court in the middle. The villa seems to be well guarded tonight – there are armed men at each side of the building, although you can’t see anyone on the roof.</npc_text>
