      <speaker_name>Lorenza</speaker_name>
      <npc_text>“&lt;Master/Mistress&gt; &lt;charname&gt;, I presume?” says a tall, graceful woman, surrounded by several frightened ladies in waiting. She smiles politely, as if greeting a proper visitor, and shows no signs of fear or discomfort.

“I was told that I should be expecting you. That you’re here to kill me,” Lorenza looks at you with feigned interest. “So tell me - is it true?”</npc_text>
