    <dlgPart>
      <portrait>Lorenza</portrait>
      <speaker_name>Lorenza</speaker_name>
      <npc_text>“How wise of you,” says Lorenza with a slight smile. “I too prefer to keep my options open until the very end. Why rush?” She gives you another smile. It’s the smile of a master being pleased with a particularly bright student.

“Since you’re undecided as of yet, may I help you make your decision? What is it you wish for? Money? Power? The forbidden knowledge? Just ask and your wildest desires will be fulfilled.”</npc_text>
