    <dlgPart>
      <portrait>Lorenza</portrait>
      <speaker_name>Lorenza</speaker_name>
      <npc_text>“Is that all you care about? Doing what you’re told and pleasing your masters? What a shame, I must say. I thought there was more to you.”</npc_text>
      <onLoadScripts />
      <answers>
        <dlgAnsw>
          <text>“In other words, you’re disappointed that I’m not eager to betray those I serve.”</text>
          <def_link>3273</def_link>
          <checkOnAppear />
          <checksOnClick />
          <linksOnClick />
