    <dlgPart>
      <portrait>Lorenza</portrait>
      <speaker_name>Lorenza</speaker_name>
      <npc_text>“You are not a dog, &lt;charname&gt;, to be proud of being loyal to those you serve. Like everything else, loyalty is good in moderation – until a better deal comes along. Well, guess what? It just did.

“So, what is it you wish for? Money? Power? The forbidden knowledge? Just ask and your wildest desires will be fulfilled.”</npc_text>
      <onLoadScripts />
      <answers>
        <dlgAnsw>
          <text>“Money? How much?”</text>
          <def_link>3281</def_link>
          <checkOnAppear />
          <checksOnClick />
          <linksOnClick />
